      "type": "header",
      "content": "International"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "intl_label",
      "label": "Section label",
      "default": "Global"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "intl_headline",
      "label": "Headline",
      "default": "One site. Every market."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "intl_body",
      "label": "Body",
      "default": "<p>Builder supports multi-language content and international layout configurations. Pages can be localized for different markets without duplicating the entire site structure.</p><p>When the website is updated, every rep's attributed links and replicated site experience reflects the update automatically. A rep in one market is never left showing customers an outdated version of the site.</p>"
